# Build context hygiene — keep the image build small + reproducible.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/.vs/
.git/
.github/
.venv/
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
spike/
tests/
docs/
deploy/
*.md
.gitignore
.dockerignore
# Web build artifacts — the SPA is built fresh inside the image from source +
# the lockfile, so the local node_modules/dist/test output never enter the context.
web/node_modules/
web/dist/
web/storybook-static/
web/test-results/
web/playwright-report/
